text: The Louisiana State University and A&M; College is a public university in Baton Rouge, Louisiana; it belongs to the Louisiana State University System of higher education as a land-grant and sea-grant institution. Colloquially, most people call the university "Louisiana State University". ==References== * ==Other websites== *Institutions of the Louisiana State University System Category:Colleges and universities in Louisiana Category:Oak Ridge Associated Universities Category:Southeastern Conference Category:Baton Rouge, Louisiana Category:1860 establishments in the United States Category:1860s establishments in Louisiana
